body.p: E. Schmidt sold the property on 87th Street, northwest corner of Stony Island Avenue, south front, 259 by 597 feet; and on 87th Street, northwest corner of Rosalie Street, south front, 244 by 597 feet, to R. A. Cepek for $27,000.
F. Bywabe sold the property on Huron Street, 244 feet east of Lincoln Street, south front, 22 by 123 feet, to A. Michalik for $4,000.
S. Kukla sold the property on Erie Street, 72 feet east of Ada Street, north front, 24 by 125 feet, to M. Wojcik for $5,800.
J. Kulik sold the property on Huron Street, 24 feet east of Avers Avenue, north front, 24 by 110 feet, to G. Lucansky for $3,500.
B. Rezabek sold the property on Whipple Street, 221 feet south of 25th Street, east front, 42 by 125 feet, to W. Kusmider for $5,500.
The Chicago Title & Trust Company sold the property in Chicago Heights, lot 10, block 14, to A. B. Svoboda for $300.
F. Vistain sold the property in Cicero, Township 39, lot 4, block 3, to J. G Piter for $2.
A. V. Clouhy sold the property in Shonts and D's Addition, lots 7 - 9, block 1, to B. Kucaba for $4,000.
A. M. Schaefer sold the property in Morton Park, H. L. and S. Company's Addition, lot 11, to F. Turek for $4,000.

F. Mathews sold the property in Stickney, New Bohemia Home Addition, lots 27
and 28, block 1, to F. Hajek for $270.
M. Vrzak sold the property on Honore Street, 221 feet south of 49th Street, east front, 24 by 124 feet, to A. Vrzak for $10.
J. Marek, Jr. sold the property on Nonore Street, 74 feet south of 60th Street, east front, $5 by 184 feet, to F. R. Gillette for $500.
P. Novak sold the property on Seeley Avenue, 215 feet north of 49th Street, east front, 24 by 124 feet, to J. Rafac for $2,100.
J. Jelinek sold the property on Blue Island Avenue, 216 feet west of Paulina Street, southeast front, 24 by 100 feet, to F. Lardotte for $10.
J. Jaros sold the property on May Street, 24 feet north of 18th Place, west front, 24 by 100 feet, to A. Pospisil for $3,900.
F. Smous sold the property on 27th Street, 94 feet east of Karlov Avenue, south front, 30 by 125 feet, to J. J. Jirka for $7,100.
J. Posedel, Jr. sold the property on Cornelia Street, 125 feet east of Campbell Avenue, north front, 25 by 124 feet, to J. Cygnar for $10.
J. Quinnert sold the property on Cortez Street, 123 feet west of Rockwell Street, south front, 34 by 120 feet, to K. Kuck for $3,750.
B. Crowley sold the property in Oak Park, Chicago Herald Addition, lot 21, block 2, to J. D. Levacek for $600.
